lv.lumii.layoutengine.flowLayout.horizontalOrdering.pqtree

Class PQTreeNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lv.lumii.layoutengine.flowLayout.horizontalOrdering.pqtree.PQTreeNode<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - object type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CNode, PNode, QNode

    public abstract class PQTreeNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements all common methods that are common to P, Q and C-type nodes.
